<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Kim_Stanley_Robinson_2005.JPG" class="image" title="Kim Stanley Robinson 2005.JPG"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b5/Kim_Stanley_Robinson_2005.JPG/250px-Kim_Stanley_Robinson_2005.JPG" width="250" height="291" border="0" /></a><br />
<small>Kim Stanley Robinson at the <a href="/wiki/63rd_World_Science_Fiction_Convention" title="63rd World Science Fiction Convention">63rd World Science Fiction Convention</a> in <a href="/wiki/Glasgow" title="Glasgow">Glasgow</a>, August 2005</small></td>
